            "id": 5897054,
            "title": "21769會是本波修正的低點嗎？廣宇⊕、鴻海、佳能、聰泰、創見",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>很多人都在問：21769 會是本波修正的低點嗎？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我認為可能還需要一些時間來確認，主要原因就是川普關稅威脅尚未完全解除，不過，對於短線的震盪，大家也無須過於緊張或擔心，畢竟台股有神功護體及基本面題材作支撐，因此，面對反覆震盪築底的過程中，各位只要把握住一個原則就是『避開山頂上的黑狗兄，買經過整理底部起漲』，其實再大的震盪都不必擔心，你說是不是？</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>產業出發成長畫夢</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>操作其實可以不一樣，我喜歡買在股價小時候，我堅持操作主流人氣股，喜歡大波段操作賺大錢，只要找對人一切都來得及！譬如：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻海集團旗下線材廠【廣宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2328-TW</a>)】</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>受惠 AI 伺服器 + 機器人雙題材加持</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>營運處在成長的浪頭上、低檔量增慣性改變</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大師兄領先市場無私與大家分享</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今日就是亮燈漲停再創新高</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>相信你們都賺到了吧</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>感謝大家共襄盛舉！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其它包括：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、品安 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、創見 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>BBU 新盛力 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4931:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4931\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4931-TW</a>)、順達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3211-TW</a>)、視覺暨自動化設備聯策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6658:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6658\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6658-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>AI 伺服器板高技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5439:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5439\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5439-TW</a>)、銘旺科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2429:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2429\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2429-TW</a>)、博智 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8155:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8155\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8155-TW</a>)、安控哲固 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3434:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3434\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3434-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航太時碩工 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4566:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4566\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4566-TW</a>)、AI 之眼佳能 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2374-TW</a>)、甚至 AI 伺服器鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\"